column5: C'mon...I have work to do today but I'm waiting for pics of the Queen Elizabeth....rocket launchers and all! Hope you had a great and safe trip to her new slip.  PICS!!! We want PICS!!!
He may still be asleep.I snapped these two pics before they set sail.
LOL, the boats name is Paultergeist, should be an ethereal experience.  Artergeist just doesn't work though.   Guess you and Art are gonna have to rename it "Rocket".
That is a sweet looking ride.  Art's & Joe are going to fun on that bad boy!  Whopper
